1
00:00:35,890 --> 00:00:38,600
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:43,208 --> 00:00:46,000
Since the Commander has spoken,

4
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,291
I won't lower myself
to argue with a nobody.

5
00:00:48,541 --> 00:00:51,041
But she trespassed into my manor

6
00:00:51,041 --> 00:00:51,916
and disturbed a noble house.

7
00:00:52,333 --> 00:00:54,125
If I let her go just like that,

8
00:00:54,291 --> 00:00:55,333
word will spread,

9
00:00:55,666 --> 00:00:58,250
and people will think
I'm easy to push around.

10
00:00:58,708 --> 00:00:59,458
Am I wrong?

11
00:01:00,125 --> 00:01:00,958
What do you want, then?

12
00:01:01,625 --> 00:01:02,583
What should I do?

13
00:01:04,375 --> 00:01:04,833
Buddy,

14
00:01:05,125 --> 00:01:05,791
help me out.

15
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:07,416
What should I do?

16
00:01:10,916 --> 00:01:11,416
I've got it.

17
00:01:12,791 --> 00:01:13,166
Hey.

18
00:01:13,916 --> 00:01:15,041
Bring that dog food here.

19
00:01:16,458 --> 00:01:18,375
You tried to use the Jinyiwei
to intimidate me.

20
00:01:18,541 --> 00:01:20,166
But no matter how powerful
the Jinyiwei are,

21
00:01:20,833 --> 00:01:23,000
they're still the Emperor's dogs.

22
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:24,458
Dogs.

23
00:01:25,458 --> 00:01:27,750
Finish this bowl of dog food,

24
00:01:28,625 --> 00:01:30,541
and I'll spare you
the charge of treason.

25
00:01:31,041 --> 00:01:31,958
You've gone too far.

26
00:01:32,333 --> 00:01:32,875
Yin Xian!

27
00:01:33,708 --> 00:01:36,333
You show no respect
for the Northern Bureau.

28
00:01:36,333 --> 00:01:38,291
Your Northern Bureau
barged into my manor.

29
00:01:38,458 --> 00:01:40,041
Did you show any respect for me?

30
00:01:41,166 --> 00:01:41,958
Zhang Weimin,

31
00:01:42,166 --> 00:01:44,416
if I report what happened today

32
00:01:45,250 --> 00:01:46,083
to His Majesty,

33
00:01:46,541 --> 00:01:48,250
you won't just lose your post.

34
00:01:48,708 --> 00:01:50,500
Your new female Jinyiwei
will be disbanded.

35
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,541
And

36
00:01:51,833 --> 00:01:53,958
this insolent Shen Bingfan

37
00:01:54,708 --> 00:01:55,708
could be beheaded as a warning.

38
00:02:01,208 --> 00:02:01,833
Marquis Taiping,

39
00:02:02,666 --> 00:02:04,166
I alone will answer for what I did.

40
00:02:04,458 --> 00:02:06,250
This has nothing to do
with the Commander or the Bureau.

41
00:02:06,708 --> 00:02:08,125
But if you think you can humiliate me,

42
00:02:08,541 --> 00:02:09,541
dream on.

43
00:02:10,875 --> 00:02:11,291
What are you doing?

44
00:02:11,291 --> 00:02:12,666
I would rather die than yield.

45
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:13,458
What are you doing?

46
00:02:13,458 --> 00:02:13,791
Don't!

47
00:02:14,291 --> 00:02:15,291
I can't drag you all down.

48
00:02:28,708 --> 00:02:30,041
Go ahead and kill yourself,

49
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:31,791
and I may spare the Northern Bureau.

50
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:42,166
Don't you dare touch her!

51
00:02:59,625 --> 00:03:00,458
- Young Master Chang!
- Bingfan!

52
00:03:01,541 --> 00:03:02,750
Are you all right?

53
00:03:04,291 --> 00:03:06,583
Young Master Chang,
what brings you here?

54
00:03:06,583 --> 00:03:07,708
Who do you think you're bullying?

55
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:08,541
I...

56
00:03:08,541 --> 00:03:10,041
Who were you trying to feed dog food?

57
00:03:11,291 --> 00:03:13,041
No, it was her problem.

58
00:03:14,125 --> 00:03:15,291
She trespassed into my manor.

59
00:03:15,875 --> 00:03:17,791
I was disciplining her
for the Commander.

60
00:03:18,541 --> 00:03:19,708
What gives you the right?

61
00:03:21,208 --> 00:03:24,166
A useless man who owes his title
to connections

62
00:03:24,541 --> 00:03:26,625
has no right to discipline

63
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,458
a Jinyiwei of the Northern Bureau.

64
00:03:33,208 --> 00:03:35,083
For a man with nothing
but borrowed status,

65
00:03:35,583 --> 00:03:36,833
you sure have a lot of nerve.

66
00:03:38,041 --> 00:03:38,541
Young Master Chang.

67
00:03:39,166 --> 00:03:40,208
It's not like that.

68
00:03:40,375 --> 00:03:42,125
She really did barge in first.

69
00:03:43,208 --> 00:03:44,333
She barged in?

70
00:03:45,083 --> 00:03:46,208
That's because a criminal

71
00:03:46,958 --> 00:03:48,375
entered your manor at night.

72
00:03:48,375 --> 00:03:50,791
She came to investigate for your safety.

73
00:03:51,291 --> 00:03:52,041
How is that barging in?

74
00:03:52,458 --> 00:03:53,541
She hadn't even reached
the front courtyard

75
00:03:53,708 --> 00:03:54,666
before you stopped her.

76
00:03:54,833 --> 00:03:56,083
You've had your fun
throwing your weight around.

77
00:03:56,416 --> 00:03:57,625
Why push it further?

78
00:03:58,375 --> 00:04:00,125
You want to report this to His Majesty?

79
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:03,666
Fine. I'll tell your cousin's husband

80
00:04:03,916 --> 00:04:05,833
and His Majesty what you've been up to.

81
00:04:06,375 --> 00:04:07,833
Let them see it for themselves.

82
00:04:07,916 --> 00:04:08,625
No, no.

83
00:04:09,125 --> 00:04:09,708
Look, Young Master Chang,

84
00:04:10,166 --> 00:04:11,041
I didn't know

85
00:04:11,375 --> 00:04:13,541
what your relationship
with Officer Shen was.

86
00:04:14,208 --> 00:04:14,500
But

87
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,958
now I understand.

88
00:04:16,375 --> 00:04:18,416
This was all a misunderstanding.

89
00:04:20,291 --> 00:04:20,750
A misunderstanding.

90
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:21,708
Really.

91
00:04:21,958 --> 00:04:23,541
Can I take her with me, then?

92
00:04:24,083 --> 00:04:24,791
Of course.

93
00:04:25,041 --> 00:04:25,458
Young Master Chang,

94
00:04:27,458 --> 00:04:28,291
please do as you wish.

95
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:46,583
Take care.

96
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:58,180
♪The past, like a song,
still echoes in my ears♪

97
00:04:58,890 --> 00:05:02,680
♪A scene of birds and dusk♪

98
00:05:03,208 --> 00:05:04,333
Why did you bring me here?

99
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:06,041
Do you understand

100
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:09,166
that the Jinyiwei
is a tightly run court agency?

101
00:05:09,541 --> 00:05:10,625
That Flying Fish Robe

102
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:12,916
and Embroidered Spring Blade
were not given lightly.

103
00:05:13,416 --> 00:05:15,750
Once you wear them,
you no longer act for yourself.

104
00:05:16,625 --> 00:05:18,291
You represent the Northern Bureau.

105
00:05:19,083 --> 00:05:20,083
Before you act,

106
00:05:20,833 --> 00:05:22,458
can you think of the bigger picture?

107
00:05:25,541 --> 00:05:27,125
I'm used to working alone.

108
00:05:27,166 --> 00:05:28,541
Then turn in your badge

109
00:05:28,833 --> 00:05:30,208
and go back to the martial world.

110
00:05:30,458 --> 00:05:32,791
You have no sense of teamwork,
and you're arrogant.

111
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:36,250
You're not fit to serve
in the Northern Bureau.

112
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:39,541
But I suspected Marquis Taiping's manor
was hiding a fugitive.

113
00:05:39,541 --> 00:05:40,958
Was it wrong to investigate?

114
00:05:40,958 --> 00:05:42,791
Do you think everything in this world

115
00:05:43,041 --> 00:05:44,750
can be done your way?

116
00:05:46,083 --> 00:05:47,333
Even His Majesty

117
00:05:48,375 --> 00:05:51,750
has things he cannot do,
no matter how much he wishes to.

118
00:05:52,708 --> 00:05:53,416
The court

119
00:05:54,375 --> 00:05:55,708
has its rules.

120
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:58,166
If you want to keep serving
in the Northern Bureau,

121
00:05:58,791 --> 00:06:00,083
learn how it works.

122
00:06:01,041 --> 00:06:03,333
If you want to stay a wandering hero,

123
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:05,666
fine. Do whatever you want.

124
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,000
But resign from the Northern Bureau.

125
00:06:12,666 --> 00:06:13,833
Does entering official service

126
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,208
really mean losing all freedom?

127
00:06:20,333 --> 00:06:20,791
Yes.

128
00:06:21,416 --> 00:06:22,958
The martial world has its rules.

129
00:06:23,833 --> 00:06:24,833
You settle debts and grudges freely,

130
00:06:25,083 --> 00:06:25,958
without restraint.

131
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:28,375
That is why I opened Chong'er Pavilion.

132
00:06:28,666 --> 00:06:29,500
To live freely.

133
00:06:30,375 --> 00:06:32,000
But once you serve the court,

134
00:06:33,625 --> 00:06:34,958
you must know where you stand.

135
00:06:35,041 --> 00:06:36,458
Your every word

136
00:06:37,791 --> 00:06:39,000
and every action
are no longer yours alone.

137
00:06:40,666 --> 00:06:42,083
You are a Jinyiwei.

138
00:06:42,791 --> 00:06:44,500
If you keep acting on your own,

139
00:06:45,208 --> 00:06:46,416
how many people will you drag down?

140
00:06:48,208 --> 00:06:50,666
If Marquis Taiping
had pressed the matter,

141
00:06:52,291 --> 00:06:53,375
the female Jinyiwei
could have been disbanded.

142
00:06:54,833 --> 00:06:55,958
What would happen to Hua Mange?

143
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,000
What would happen to Cheng Xintian?

144
00:06:57,541 --> 00:06:58,250
Did you ever think of that?

145
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,125
(Northern Bureau)

146
00:07:09,125 --> 00:07:10,166
(Northern Bureau)
I overstepped.

147
00:07:10,833 --> 00:07:12,458
I acted rashly as the Jinyiwei

148
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,541
and forced my way
into Marquis Taiping's manor.

149
00:07:13,916 --> 00:07:16,041
I put the Northern Bureau at risk.
I deserve punishment.

150
00:07:16,833 --> 00:07:17,833
Please punish me, my lord.

151
00:07:18,791 --> 00:07:19,708
Shen Bingfan,

152
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:22,791
that was reckless.

153
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:25,583
You dared provoke Marquis Taiping,
Yin Xian.

154
00:07:25,833 --> 00:07:26,875
Do you know

155
00:07:26,875 --> 00:07:29,041
what a dangerous schemer he is?

156
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:32,000
I only wanted to catch the criminal.

157
00:07:32,541 --> 00:07:34,083
I forgot who I was dealing with.

158
00:07:34,458 --> 00:07:35,125
Naive!

159
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,750
Extremely naive!

160
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:40,458
Even if you saw

161
00:07:40,833 --> 00:07:41,583
Diaotu

162
00:07:41,958 --> 00:07:43,416
enter Marquis Taiping's manor,

163
00:07:43,708 --> 00:07:44,750
even if you found out

164
00:07:45,166 --> 00:07:47,375
that Yin Xian was sheltering him,

165
00:07:47,875 --> 00:07:49,291
what could you do to him?

166
00:07:50,125 --> 00:07:51,583
Without solid proof,

167
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:53,375
you can't touch him.

168
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,708
To bring down

169
00:07:56,041 --> 00:07:58,375
a first-rank marquis
appointed by the court

170
00:07:59,291 --> 00:08:00,416
is no simple matter.

171
00:08:01,166 --> 00:08:02,000
I understand my mistake.

172
00:08:06,166 --> 00:08:06,791
Enough.

173
00:08:07,916 --> 00:08:08,791
Since you know you were wrong,

174
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,166
I won't punish you.

175
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,583
Remember.

176
00:08:14,416 --> 00:08:15,208
Do not let it happen again.

177
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:17,875
Thank you, my lord.

178
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:22,333
But Diaotu has disappeared.

179
00:08:22,666 --> 00:08:23,416
What do we do now?

180
00:08:25,583 --> 00:08:27,750
Since we've already spooked him,

181
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:29,541
for now,

182
00:08:30,333 --> 00:08:31,083
we do nothing.

183
00:08:31,416 --> 00:08:31,833
But

184
00:08:32,666 --> 00:08:34,083
if the ten-day deadline comes,

185
00:08:34,791 --> 00:08:36,208
how do we answer the court?

186
00:08:36,375 --> 00:08:38,041
That is my problem.

187
00:08:39,541 --> 00:08:41,166
I've caused you trouble.

188
00:08:42,458 --> 00:08:45,041
Since we've alarmed Diaotu,

189
00:08:46,041 --> 00:08:49,291
he likely won't strike again
anytime soon.

190
00:08:49,958 --> 00:08:51,125
But you female Jinyiwei

191
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:51,916
must remember this.

192
00:08:52,666 --> 00:08:53,791
Do everything you can

193
00:08:53,875 --> 00:08:56,000
to capture Diaotu,
the Flower-Picking Bee.

194
00:08:56,416 --> 00:08:58,250
Only then will your place

195
00:08:58,458 --> 00:09:00,000
as female Jinyiwei be secure.

196
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:04,208
And I may save some face.

197
00:09:07,416 --> 00:09:08,958
If I fail to bring Diaotu in,

198
00:09:08,958 --> 00:09:10,541
I will leave the Jinyiwei.

199
00:09:18,916 --> 00:09:21,333
You caused quite a mess this time.

200
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:23,958
I was too reckless this time.

201
00:09:24,083 --> 00:09:24,875
It won't happen again.

202
00:09:25,125 --> 00:09:25,958
Good.

203
00:09:26,541 --> 00:09:27,416
From now on,

204
00:09:27,791 --> 00:09:29,625
discuss things with us first.

205
00:09:29,958 --> 00:09:32,291
More heads mean more ideas.

206
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:34,333
But

207
00:09:34,458 --> 00:09:36,666
this does make me wonder.

208
00:09:37,333 --> 00:09:37,875
About what?

209
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:40,916
Who exactly is Chang Beiming?

210
00:09:41,458 --> 00:09:44,083
Why did someone as arrogant
as Marquis Taiping

211
00:09:44,833 --> 00:09:46,750
turn frightened before him?

212
00:09:47,916 --> 00:09:49,291
You have a point.

213
00:09:50,208 --> 00:09:50,916
But

214
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:52,750
I have a question too.

215
00:09:53,416 --> 00:09:55,708
That day, when you used your footwork,

216
00:09:56,208 --> 00:09:57,791
why did I hear a cat meow in midair?

217
00:09:58,166 --> 00:09:58,666
(I'll go after him.)

218
00:09:58,666 --> 00:09:59,208
(Are you all right?)

219
00:09:59,458 --> 00:10:00,041
(I'm fine.)

220
00:10:00,041 --> 00:10:01,125
(Hua, be careful!)

221
00:10:10,208 --> 00:10:10,958
What? I don't think so.

222
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:13,166
Funny.

223
00:10:14,083 --> 00:10:16,250
You must have heard wrong.

224
00:10:17,833 --> 00:10:19,125
Maybe I'm overthinking it.

225
00:10:21,166 --> 00:10:22,166
Bingfan,

226
00:10:23,541 --> 00:10:24,500
I think

227
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,708
our top priority now

228
00:10:27,208 --> 00:10:28,666
is catching Diaotu.

229
00:10:29,375 --> 00:10:30,541
You're right.

230
00:10:37,458 --> 00:10:37,916
Yeah.

231
00:10:38,333 --> 00:10:38,833
Wait.

232
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:40,875
If I lose this round,

233
00:10:40,875 --> 00:10:42,208
your monthly pay is gone.

234
00:10:44,791 --> 00:10:45,708
Squad Leader Shen.

235
00:10:51,458 --> 00:10:52,666
Why is Marquis Taiping afraid of you?

236
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:56,958
Have you forgotten yesterday?

237
00:10:58,208 --> 00:10:59,250
I haven't forgiven you yet.

238
00:10:59,458 --> 00:11:00,625
And now you're interrogating me?

239
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:04,041
Yin Xian isn't even
afraid of the Commander.

240
00:11:04,041 --> 00:11:05,000
Why would he fear you?

241
00:11:05,333 --> 00:11:06,458
That

242
00:11:08,625 --> 00:11:09,333
is a good question.

243
00:11:12,416 --> 00:11:14,708
As they say, evil never beats good,

244
00:11:14,708 --> 00:11:17,083
and right is on my side.

245
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,625
I want the truth.

246
00:11:21,625 --> 00:11:22,458
The truth

247
00:11:23,166 --> 00:11:23,958
is...

248
00:11:29,625 --> 00:11:30,333
Guess.

249
00:11:34,041 --> 00:11:35,166
Does he owe you money too?

250
00:11:35,625 --> 00:11:36,583
As if he's worthy.

251
00:11:37,208 --> 00:11:37,833
What?

252
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,083
I mean,

253
00:11:42,208 --> 00:11:44,041
yes, exactly.

254
00:11:44,625 --> 00:11:45,250
Smart girl.

255
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,958
If you won't tell me, fine.

256
00:11:49,416 --> 00:11:50,208
I'll find out myself.

257
00:11:56,291 --> 00:11:58,875
(I only meant to sneak into the Bureau,
destroy the records, and leave.)

258
00:11:59,958 --> 00:12:02,375
(Why have I started enjoying this life?)

259
00:12:03,416 --> 00:12:04,125
(Could it be)

260
00:12:04,916 --> 00:12:07,166
(that those two girls
have gotten to me?)

261
00:12:10,083 --> 00:12:11,375
The Northern Bureau

262
00:12:11,666 --> 00:12:14,375
abused its power
and insulted imperial kin.

263
00:12:14,416 --> 00:12:15,916
(Submitted by Yin Xian, Marquis Taiping)
Without an edict or gold token,

264
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,583
(Northern Bureau)
they forced their way into my manor

265
00:12:17,583 --> 00:12:20,208
(Northern Bureau)
and accused me of harboring a fugitive.

266
00:12:20,708 --> 00:12:23,250
I beg Your Majesty for justice.

267
00:12:24,875 --> 00:12:26,041
An imperial edict arrives.

268
00:12:27,375 --> 00:12:28,750
By the Mandate of Heaven,

269
00:12:29,208 --> 00:12:31,208
the Emperor decrees:

270
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:33,500
Marquis Taiping, Yin Xian,

271
00:12:33,708 --> 00:12:35,750
has accused the Northern Bureau

272
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:38,958
of overstepping its rank
and insulting imperial kin,

273
00:12:39,166 --> 00:12:42,708
gravely damaging imperial authority
and the court's dignity.

274
00:12:43,208 --> 00:12:44,541
They violated the law,

275
00:12:44,541 --> 00:12:47,333
abused their power, and disrupted order.

276
00:12:47,791 --> 00:12:49,166
Upon receipt of this edict,

277
00:12:49,166 --> 00:12:53,416
Jinyiwei Commander Zhang Weimin
shall enter court at once

278
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:57,708
and explain the matter to the Cabinet.
By imperial order.

279
00:12:58,625 --> 00:13:01,208
Absurd. Absolutely absurd.

280
00:13:02,791 --> 00:13:03,958
I deserve death for my mistake.

281
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:05,875
Your usual arrogance

282
00:13:06,083 --> 00:13:07,750
and disrespect for your peers
is one thing.

283
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:10,000
But this time,
you provoked the wrong man.

284
00:13:10,708 --> 00:13:11,458
If the court blames us,

285
00:13:12,541 --> 00:13:13,458
I will bear it alone.

286
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:15,000
Zuo Da. Jiang Biao.

287
00:13:15,375 --> 00:13:15,791
Yes.

288
00:13:16,416 --> 00:13:18,458
Take Shen Bingfan's saber and badge.

289
00:13:19,458 --> 00:13:20,666
When the Commander returns,

290
00:13:20,833 --> 00:13:21,458
we will decide her punishment.

291
00:13:27,041 --> 00:13:27,625
Everyone's here!

292
00:13:42,833 --> 00:13:44,958
The Northern Bureau
has caused quite a stir

293
00:13:45,333 --> 00:13:46,708
and disgraced the Jinyiwei.

294
00:13:49,958 --> 00:13:50,583
Mr. Duan,

295
00:13:51,208 --> 00:13:53,958
you came to laugh at the Bureau,
didn't you?

296
00:13:54,666 --> 00:13:55,458
Zhang Weimin,

297
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,250
Marquis Taiping has accused you

298
00:13:57,541 --> 00:13:58,583
of indulging your subordinates,

299
00:13:58,958 --> 00:14:00,166
disturbing his manor,

300
00:14:00,958 --> 00:14:02,125
and insulting imperial kin.

301
00:14:02,583 --> 00:14:03,166
My lord,

302
00:14:03,375 --> 00:14:04,791
that is an exaggeration.

303
00:14:05,416 --> 00:14:07,041
Then give me the modest version.

304
00:14:07,208 --> 00:14:08,666
Isn't this your fault?

305
00:14:08,833 --> 00:14:09,416
What?

306
00:14:09,583 --> 00:14:10,875
Now you're twisting the facts?

307
00:14:10,875 --> 00:14:12,333
You were the ones

308
00:14:12,333 --> 00:14:13,625
who forced me into this.

309
00:14:13,833 --> 00:14:16,000
You gave me ten days

310
00:14:16,250 --> 00:14:17,958
to catch that predator Diaotu.

311
00:14:18,041 --> 00:14:20,583
After Diaotu slipped
into Marquis Taiping's manor,

312
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:23,166
whether Yin Xian knew it or not,

313
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,958
I had to send someone to check.

314
00:14:25,375 --> 00:14:27,083
For his safety, of course.

315
00:14:27,708 --> 00:14:30,333
Who knew Marquis Taiping
would reject my goodwill,

316
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:31,791
then go to His Majesty

317
00:14:31,958 --> 00:14:34,083
and the Cabinet to file a complaint
against me?

318
00:14:34,541 --> 00:14:35,291
What do we call that?

319
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:35,875
That is...

320
00:14:36,791 --> 00:14:38,041
That is biting the hand that helps you!

321
00:14:38,208 --> 00:14:38,791
Am I wrong?

322
00:14:41,166 --> 00:14:42,458
From what I heard,

323
00:14:42,833 --> 00:14:44,875
that is not how it happened.

324
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:49,125
It was Shen Bingfan,
your newly recruited female Jinyiwei.

325
00:14:50,458 --> 00:14:53,125
She stormed into the Marquis's manor

326
00:14:53,666 --> 00:14:56,291
and demanded to search it by force.

327
00:14:59,291 --> 00:15:00,166
Let me tell you.

328
00:15:00,625 --> 00:15:02,083
That is only one side of the story.

329
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:04,875
Grand Secretary, please have some tea.

330
00:15:11,375 --> 00:15:12,166
What happened was

331
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,916
a few careless words.

332
00:15:14,708 --> 00:15:17,250
She only talked back
to Marquis Taiping a little.

333
00:15:17,458 --> 00:15:18,000
That's all.

334
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:20,208
A man of Marquis Taiping's status

335
00:15:20,208 --> 00:15:21,625
should be magnanimous.

336
00:15:21,916 --> 00:15:24,291
Surely he would not stoop to arguing
with a young woman.

337
00:15:24,291 --> 00:15:26,625
If he really did,

338
00:15:27,125 --> 00:15:29,958
it would hardly befit a first-rank lord.

339
00:15:30,208 --> 00:15:31,208
Am I right, Grand Secretary?

340
00:15:33,125 --> 00:15:33,875
I have heard

341
00:15:34,416 --> 00:15:37,708
the Commander of the Northern Bureau
always protects his own people.

342
00:15:37,958 --> 00:15:40,958
Now I see the rumors were true.

343
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:43,666
My lord,

344
00:15:44,666 --> 00:15:46,583
even if this was a misunderstanding,

345
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,458
it remains true

346
00:15:48,583 --> 00:15:51,166
that Shen Bingfan disturbed
the marquis's manor.

347
00:15:51,708 --> 00:15:53,416
Marquis Taiping has complained
to His Majesty.

348
00:15:54,333 --> 00:15:55,958
His Majesty has asked about it.

349
00:15:56,583 --> 00:15:58,750
The Cabinet is in a difficult position.

350
00:15:58,833 --> 00:15:59,333
How about this?

351
00:15:59,666 --> 00:16:01,750
Go back and punish Shen Bingfan.

352
00:16:02,375 --> 00:16:03,833
Give Marquis Taiping an answer.

353
00:16:04,166 --> 00:16:04,791
Then

354
00:16:05,416 --> 00:16:06,083
I

355
00:16:06,583 --> 00:16:07,708
will mediate

356
00:16:08,708 --> 00:16:09,791
and smooth this over.

357
00:16:10,416 --> 00:16:11,583
How does that sound?

358
00:16:15,125 --> 00:16:15,458
My lord,

359
00:16:16,208 --> 00:16:17,000
please

360
00:16:17,541 --> 00:16:18,166
have some water.

361
00:16:21,875 --> 00:16:24,375
But do not cover for your own people.

362
00:16:25,750 --> 00:16:26,333
Rest assured.

363
00:16:27,333 --> 00:16:28,958
I will punish her severely.

364
00:16:28,958 --> 00:16:31,500
She won't... There will be no next time.

365
00:16:31,916 --> 00:16:32,916
That's more like it.

366
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,166
Bring in Shen Bingfan,
the offending officer.

367
00:16:35,166 --> 00:16:36,270
(Northern Bureau)

368
00:16:42,208 --> 00:16:43,458
Greetings, Commander.

369
00:16:43,791 --> 00:16:46,041
Shen Bingfan, you overstepped your rank

370
00:16:46,333 --> 00:16:47,375
and disturbed a marquis's manor.

371
00:16:47,875 --> 00:16:48,666
I

372
00:16:49,375 --> 00:16:50,666
must punish you severely.

373
00:16:53,083 --> 00:16:54,041
Do you accept this?

374
00:16:55,083 --> 00:16:55,958
I know my fault.

375
00:16:56,333 --> 00:16:57,250
I accept any punishment.

376
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:59,208
Good. In that case,

377
00:16:59,833 --> 00:17:00,958
I will punish you

378
00:17:03,291 --> 00:17:04,291
by docking three months' pay.

379
00:17:05,083 --> 00:17:06,208
Let this be a warning.

380
00:17:09,041 --> 00:17:11,333
My lord, only three months' pay?

381
00:17:11,375 --> 00:17:12,125
That's too light.

382
00:17:12,166 --> 00:17:13,250
What do you mean?

383
00:17:13,333 --> 00:17:15,583
Try losing three months' pay yourself.

384
00:17:15,583 --> 00:17:17,416
I did nothing wrong. Why punish me?

385
00:17:18,041 --> 00:17:20,541
My lord, if you keep
favoring them like this,

386
00:17:20,791 --> 00:17:21,666
if the Cabinet

387
00:17:21,875 --> 00:17:23,500
or the Southern Bureau finds out...

388
00:17:24,458 --> 00:17:27,333
What scumbag would dare
gossip about this?

389
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:30,041
I'm punishing her according to the law.

390
00:17:30,750 --> 00:17:31,541
Guokai,

391
00:17:31,916 --> 00:17:35,041
you must open your mind. Open it.

392
00:17:35,875 --> 00:17:36,666
Open it!

393
00:17:37,375 --> 00:17:38,916
If you show no care
for your subordinates,

394
00:17:39,333 --> 00:17:41,041
who will risk their lives for you later?

395
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:45,291
Thank you for your mercy, Commander.

396
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:46,750
My lord.

397
00:17:48,583 --> 00:17:50,333
Bingfan, what brings you here?

398
00:17:51,541 --> 00:17:53,333
I came to thank you again
for protecting me.

399
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:56,166
You shouldn't thank me.

400
00:17:56,458 --> 00:17:57,166
It was

401
00:17:57,625 --> 00:17:59,625
Chang Beiming who spoke up for you.

402
00:17:59,916 --> 00:18:00,541
Otherwise,

403
00:18:01,083 --> 00:18:01,916
I would have punished you harshly.

404
00:18:03,458 --> 00:18:05,250
Who exactly is Chang Beiming?

405
00:18:06,041 --> 00:18:08,500
Why would even the Grand Secretary
show him respect?

406
00:18:10,083 --> 00:18:12,166
You two live right next door.

407
00:18:13,708 --> 00:18:14,875
You should ask him.

408
00:18:20,041 --> 00:18:20,875
(Went home?)

409
00:18:21,375 --> 00:18:22,458
(Isn't this his home?)

410
00:18:22,541 --> 00:18:23,541
(Of course not.)

411
00:18:23,875 --> 00:18:25,166
(This is the young master's business.)

412
00:18:25,166 --> 00:18:26,166
(He has another residence.)

413
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:29,041
(My young master is mainly worried
about you, Miss Shen.)

414
00:18:29,333 --> 00:18:30,625
(He went home to settle this for you.)

415
00:18:48,930 --> 00:18:52,100
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

416
00:18:52,470 --> 00:18:55,850
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

417
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:59,100
♪My heart drifted lost♪

418
00:18:59,100 --> 00:19:02,510
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

419
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:06,810
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

420
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:10,560
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

421
00:19:11,140 --> 00:19:13,350
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

422
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:17,390
♪I've softly let it go♪

423
00:19:17,390 --> 00:19:21,260
♪The vow you made was true♪

424
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:25,010
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

425
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:27,220
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

426
00:19:27,220 --> 00:19:31,760
♪And forget at world's end♪

427
00:19:32,060 --> 00:19:33,560
♪Embracing memory♪

428
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:35,930
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

429
00:19:35,930 --> 00:19:39,810
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

430
00:19:39,810 --> 00:19:42,140
♪I wish to let it pass♪

431
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:47,140
♪And run toward this vast life♪

